  "text": "Kanji [CITATION_1] offers a solution to some of these problems such as tracking financial results while simultaneously monitoring progress in building the capabilities and acquiring the intangible assets needed for future growth and stability and reducing information overload. Other questions are where to set the system boundaries and how to include external measures, for example, to measure market shares and customer satisfaction.",
